## Scope notes

This license covers the DSH (Dome Sovereign Hub) shell, framework, setup
scripts, agent-stack scaffolding, and documentation in this repository.

It does NOT cover:

- Trinity Consortium proprietary components (FRACTAL E8-SSII-AGI engine
  internals, Mycelium Neural Mesh protocols, sovereign node cryptographic
  identity) — those are governed by Trinity Consortium terms.
- Third-party dependencies — governed by their respective licenses
  (see `package.json`, `compute/requirements.txt`).
- Model weights downloaded at setup time (e.g. Sentence-Transformers,
  Ollama models) — governed by each model's license.

If you plan to use DSH commercially or integrate it with Trinity Consortium
infrastructure, consult `docs/PUBLIC_PROD_HARDENING.md` and contact the
copyright holder for Trinity-specific terms.
